  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to describe the impact of a training in therapeutic education on the relation
      between a caregiver and his/her patients.

      Subjects are recruited among health professionals attending a training in therapeutic
      education. Then they are asked to identify up to 5 of their patients to be contacted by the
      researcher for an interview.

      Individual semi-structured interviews are conducted with 20 duo &quot;caregivers / patients&quot;
      before the training, 1 month and 6 months after the training.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
